{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468390/extras/banner_logo.png?t=1737483890\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>I've been trying to contact someone out there, if someone can hear me, please answer me and connect to my core.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Won't you\u00a0accept my call? Won't you enter\u00a0a\u00a0new\u00a0world?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Wishbind is an exploration based, hand-crafted 2D platformer collect-a-thon, in which you'll explore a vast world to gather a special kind of leaf essence, while interacting with  characters and discovering many secrets throughout the locale.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore a hand-crafted world in search of a special kind of leaf in a non-linear way!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use a wide array of available moves to overcome platforming challenges for different rewards!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Follow the story of some NPCs!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find unlockable colors for your character!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enter photo mode to take screenshots of your gameplay at almost any time!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Search every last corner of the map to find hidden secrets and easter eggs!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enjoy the game either in english, or spanish!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cute animals!</p></li></ul>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3468390?t=1737483890","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468390/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1737483890","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468390/0aa772ae141b5447322505e392531361c289e1c3/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737483890","capsule_imagev5":"h